  "title": "HR Executive (Payroll/ West) #HZO",
  "description": "<p>Location: Tuas <br />Salary: up to $5K + Transport allowance <br /><br /><strong>Job Scope: </strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for payroll & CPF contributions for all employees under Singapore / Malaysia employment.</li><li>Advertising and sourcing of available positions.</li><li>Arranging interviews, screening, and trainings where necessary.</li><li>Ensuring all government regulations regarding foreign hires are followed.</li><li>Guiding Workers through onboarding orientations and exit interviews.</li><li>Ensuring new hires are in the Facial Recognition System.</li><li>Internship Management </li><li>Liaise with local institutions to source and recruit interns </li><li>Coordinate intern interviews, screening, onboarding, and required training programs </li><li>Ensure full compliance with government regulations and legal requirements for foreign interns and hires Oversee and guide interns throughout the internship program </li><li>Prepare and compile HR and other ad-hoc reports.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Min. Diploma/ Degree in HR or any field </li><li>Min. 1-2 years relevant payroll experience </li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please send your updated resume to: melissa@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>All candidates’ information will be treated with the strictest confidence</p><p>Melissa Zhang Zhiqi (Mezzo)</p><p>R2197564</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>99C4599</p>",
